CatDescriptText: An article appeared in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, on July 25, 1970 featuring this or one of the related images. It was of the Harper family reunion and was published in the Courier's national edition.
TitMainTitle: Harper family reunion, including brothers and sisters Wilda Harper Sellers, Ernie Harper, Nate Harper, Alice Harper Ellis, Doris Harper Bowdry, Chuck Harper, Mrs. Austin, unknown woman, and Walt Harper, gathered around picnic table with patio umbrella, in Pittsburgh
